sources.title: 4K - Earth's Final Fury (1979) THEIR LIVES BECAME A LIVING HELL | Science fiction film
sources.description:
Aliens visit the solar-powered house of a middle-class family, and the house is suddenly sucked into a time warp that transports it back to prehistoric times.

Original title: The Day Time Ended (1979)

Directed by John Cardos

Main cast:
Jim Davis - Grant Williams
Dorothy Malone - Ana Williams
Christopher Mitchum - Richard Williams
Marcy Lafferty - Beth Williams
Scott Kolden - Steve Williams
Natasha Ryan - Jenny Williams
Roberto Contreras - Gas Station Attendant
